00:32.732 --> 00:33.867
Look out!

00:35.301 --> 00:36.539
Oh, my God!

00:36.541 --> 00:38.371
Did we hit it?

00:38.373 --> 00:39.907
Looks okay to me.

00:39.909 --> 00:41.811
This is Riley.
The Kealoha's dog.

00:41.813 --> 00:42.876
Babe, we should go.

00:42.878 --> 00:44.812
We can't just leave him.

00:44.814 --> 00:46.748
Hello?

00:46.750 --> 00:47.884
Mrs. Kealoha?

00:47.886 --> 00:49.189
We found Riley.
Are you home?

00:49.191 --> 00:50.717
Hello?

00:50.719 --> 00:52.453
Is anybody home?

00:52.455 --> 00:54.294
Hello?

00:54.296 --> 00:55.590
Mrs. Kealoha?

00:55.592 --> 00:57.727
Are you home?

00:57.729 --> 00:58.927
Anybody?

01:00.233 --> 01:02.600
Hello?

01:02.602 --> 01:04.641
Hello? Mrs. Kealoha?

01:04.643 --> 01:06.842
Are you home?

01:19.391 --> 01:22.999
